#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:698
msgid ""
"If you choose to increase performance, and you can install mod_perl, then "
"you can leave mod_cgi off, and configure the <application>apache</"
"application> web server for use with mod_perl, in the following manner."
msgstr ""
"Zur Verbesserung der Performance können sie mod_cgi deaktivieren und den "
"<application>Apache</application> Webserver stattdessen für die Benutzung "
"von Mod_Perl konfigurieren."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/installation-and-basic-configuration.xml:705
msgid ""
"Please ensure that mod_perl is installed and loaded, in order to take "
"advantage of this feature. Due to the nature of the start-up script, your "
"server will not fail to start, if the mod_perl is not properly loaded or "
"compiled in your apache web server, unless mod_cgi is also on. Technically "
"speaking you can leave mod_cgi on as well, but you should not."
msgstr ""
"Stellen Sie bitte sicher, daß mod_perl installiert und geladen ist. "
"Andernfalls wird der Webserver-Dienst trotzdem starten, in diesem Fall wird "
"jedoch mod_cgi verwendet, wenn es noch aktiviert ist (Deaktivierung wird "
"empfohlen)."

