#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:514
msgid ""
"You can search for a registered customer, edit his data by clicking on his "
"name.  You also have the possibility to change the customer back-end, for "
"further information please refer to the chapter about <link linkend="
"\"external-backends\"> external back-ends </link>."
