#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:540
msgid ""
"The customer can access to the system by providing his username and "
"password. The CustomerID is needed by the system to identify the user and "
"his tickets. Since the email address is a unique value, it can be used as ID."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:547
msgid ""
"To keep the consistency of the data for OTRS it is not possible to delete "
"customers, but only deactivate them. To do so, set them to "
