msgid ""
"Through the link \"Queue\" of the admin area, you can manage the <link "
"linkend=\"what-is-a-queue\"> queues </link> of your system (see Figure 5.18 "
"below). In a new OTRS installation there are 4 default queues: Junk, Misc, "
"Postmaster and Raw. All incoming messages will be stored in it the \"Raw\" "
"queue if no filter rules are defined. The \"Junk\" queue can be used to "
"store spam messages."
msgstr ""

