#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:896
msgid ""
"Like salutations, signatures can also contain dynamical content (e.g. the "
"first and last name of the agent who answers the ticket), also variables "
"replace the content of the signature text for every ticket. See the lower "
"part of the signatures screen for the variables which can be used. If you "
"include the variable &lt;OTRS_LAST_NAME&gt; in a signature for example, the "
"last name of the agent who answers the ticket will replace the variable's "
