"From OTRS 2.1 on, it is possible to define a person responsible for a "
"ticket, additionally to its owner. Moreover, all activities connected with "
"the ticket can be watched. These two functionalities are implemented with "
"the TicketResponsible and TicketWatcher features, and facilitate the "
