#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/smime.xml:246
msgid ""
"This part of the setup is carried out in the admin area, block system, "
"choosing the menu item <link linkend=\"adminarea-smime\"> \"SMIME\" </"
"link> . In case the general S/MIME support in OTRS has not yet been enabled, "
"the mask points this out to the administrator and provides a comfortable "
"link for that purpose."
