msgid ""
"With the SysConfig group <link linkend=\"Framework:Crypt::SMIME\"> \"Crypt::"
"SMIME\" </link> , you can also enable and configure the general S/MIME "
"support."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/smime.xml:268
msgid ""
"Here you can activate the S/MIME support, define the paths for the OpenSSL "
"command and the directory for the certificates. The key file created above "
