#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/smime.xml:288
msgid ""
"Obviously, all public S/MIME keys of communication partners can be imported "
"using the <link linkend=\"adminarea-customers\"> customer administration "
"tool </link> as well, when creating a new entry or modifying an existing one."
