#: en/stats.xml:1287
msgid "Automated stat generation - Cronjob"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/stats.xml:1290
msgid ""
"It obviously does not really make sense to generate stats manually in the "
"command line, as the stat module has a convenient graphical user interface. "
"However, generating stats manually does make sense when combined with a "
"Cronjob."
